Package: hedgehog
Type: Package
Title: Hedgehog - Property Testing in R
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-03-02
Authors@R: person("Huw", "Campbell", email = "huw.campbell@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Hedgehog is a modern property-based
  testing system, in the spirit of QuickCheck.
  Hedgehog uses integrated shrinking, so shrinks
  obey the invariants of generated values by
  construction.
License: MIT + file LICENCE
Imports: purrr
Depends: testthat
Suggests: R6, knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
